OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F304A1779678250
OL,3,CTech giants earn up to #194,000 from
OL,4,Cdata of each UK internet user, study
OL,5,Cfinds
OL,7,FBig technology and artificial
OL,8,Fintelligence (AI) firms earn up to
OL,9,F#194,000 from using the data of each
OL,10,FUK internet user over their lifetime,
OL,11,Faccording to new analysis.
OL,13,FSome of the world's biggest and most
OL,14,Fpowerful companies collect and
OL,15,Fmonetise personal data to power the
OL,16,Finternet, Web3 Foundation found in a
OL,17,Freport.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G1/8
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
