FL,305,300,200,140,000,100
PN,30402
SC,0002
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F304A1779678250
OL,3,CTech giants earn up to #194,000 from
OL,4,Cdata of each UK internet user, study
OL,5,Cfinds
OL,7,FThe study looked at a vast range of
OL,8,Fways that people leave a digital
OL,9,Ffootprint, from search queries, clicks
OL,10,Fand location signals, through to
OL,11,Fonline purchases, messages, uploaded
OL,12,Fimages and social media posts.
OL,14,FTypically, this information has been
OL,15,Fcollected through technology like
OL,16,Fcookies and used to help companies
OL,17,Fcreate targeted adverts.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G2/8
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,305,300,200,140,000,100
PN,30403
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F304A1779678250
OL,3,CTech giants earn up to #194,000 from
OL,4,Cdata of each UK internet user, study
OL,5,Cfinds
OL,7,FBut the research found that people's
OL,8,Fdata is increasingly being collected,
OL,9,Faggregated and analysed for newer
OL,10,Fforms of monetisation like building AI
OL,11,Fsystems and training models.
OL,13,FIt estimates that each UK and European
OL,14,Finternet user contributes up to
OL,15,F#194,000 in inflation-linked
OL,16,Fcommercial value over their digital
OL,17,Flifetimes.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G3/8
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,305,300,200,140,000,100
PN,30404
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F304A1779678250
OL,3,CTech giants earn up to #194,000 from
OL,4,Cdata of each UK internet user, study
OL,5,Cfinds
OL,7,FRather than pointing to a specific
OL,8,Famount of money that people
OL,9,Fcontribute, the modelling aims to
OL,10,Fdemonstrate the scale at which the
OL,11,Finternet is powered by people's data,
OL,12,Faccording to the report.
OL,14,FBill Laboon, vice president of
OL,15,Ftechnical operations for Web3
OL,16,FFoundation, told the Press
OL,17,FAssociation: "People should be aware
OL,18,Fthat their data is being used and
OL,19,Fmonetised by all kinds of other
OL,20,Fentities.
OL,26,@yD@NOU
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G4/8
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,305,300,200,140,000,100
PN,30405
SC,0005
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F304A1779678250
OL,3,CTech giants earn up to #194,000 from
OL,4,Cdata of each UK internet user, study
OL,5,Cfinds
OL,7,F"It's a privacy issue. Likely people
OL,8,Fdo not understand or realise that
OL,9,Fwhenever they're asking a question on
OL,10,FChatGPT, when they are selecting a
OL,11,Fspell check correction... that's being
OL,12,Fused."
OL,14,FHe said targeted advertising was the
OL,15,Fmore "classic" way that people
OL,16,Funderstand their data is used, but
OL,17,Fthey may be less aware that it is
OL,18,Fbecoming the "lifeblood" of AI
OL,19,Ftraining models.
OL,26,@oD@AOUtD@FO]wD@FOUwD@NO]zD@NOUzD@XO]
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G5/8
