PN,30406
SC,0006
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F304A1779678250
OL,3,CTech giants earn up to #194,000 from
OL,4,Cdata of each UK internet user, study
OL,5,Cfinds
OL,7,FWeb3 Foundation, an internet
OL,8,Fchallenger which aims to replace the
OL,9,Fcurrent web with a new user-led
OL,10,Fsystem, said people may be being
OL,11,Fexcluded from the AI systems that
OL,12,Ftheir information helped to build.
OL,14,FTechnology giants Amazon, Alphabet,
OL,15,FAnthropic, Microsoft and Meta are
OL,16,Festimated to earn up to #1,000
OL,17,Fannually on a single internet user,
OL,18,Fthe report found.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G6/8
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,305,300,200,140,000,100
PN,30407
SC,0007
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F304A1779678250
OL,3,CTech giants earn up to #194,000 from
OL,4,Cdata of each UK internet user, study
OL,5,Cfinds
OL,7,FThis means that other growing AI firms
OL,8,Fare "doing the heavy lifting" when it
OL,9,Fcomes to using personal data and
OL,10,Fpotentially earning more.
OL,12,FUS chip-maker Nvidia was the first
OL,13,Fcompany in the world to reach a market
OL,14,Fvalue of five trillion US dollars
OL,15,F(#3.72 trillion) last year, having
OL,16,Fstruck deals with AI giants like
OL,17,FOpenAI and Oracle.
OL,19,FMicrosoft and Apple have also recently
OL,20,Fsurpassed the four trillion US dollar
OL,21,F(#2.98 trillion) valuation mark.
OL,26,@pD@EOUpD@]O]
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G7/8
