OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F304A1779678250
OL,3,CTech giants earn up to #194,000 from
OL,4,Cdata of each UK internet user, study
OL,5,Cfinds
OL,7,F"As AI accelerates and data becomes
OL,8,Feven more valuable, building a more
OL,9,Ftransparent, user-led internet is
OL,10,Fbecoming increasingly urgent," Mr
OL,11,FLaboon added.
